summary:
People see me as a friendly, responsible and  solution focused person.
I can set up priorities that best suit my working environment but I am also someone who loves working in a team to accomplish company's  goals. 
Leading people is what I am very comfortable with because I give them the chance to express themselves and their talents. 
In addition, I am very trustful and would like to work in the shipping and Logistics sectors.
